nodes.text: Senache was a male individual who 204th Imperial Fighter Wing commanding officer Colonel Shakara Nuress cared about and considered beautiful and dear to her. At some point during Nuress' service to the Galactic Empire, Senache suffered from a disease that rotted his heart and although he fought the illness, he eventually succumbed to it and died. Nuress stayed by Senache's side until his death and considered the personal loss as painful as any military loss.
